  "method": [
    "Preheat the oven to 350°.",
    "Take a skillet, and cook onion and beef over the medium heat.",
    "Add seasonings and flour.",
    "Stir in tomatoes and bring it to boil. Lower the heat, then simmer for",
    "15 minutes.",
    "Heat butter in a pan over the medium heat.",
    "Cook garlic in it for around 1 minute. Mix flour, and blend it",
    "gradually.",
    "Add broth, and bring it to boil. Cook for almost 2 minutes.",
    "Add seasonings and tomato sauce.",
    "Pour sauce into a baking dish. Place beef mixture on each tortilla.",
    "Add cheese on top of it.",
    "Top with some more sauce.",
    "Bake it covered for around 30-35 minutes.",
    "Then add the remaining cheese.",
    "Bake it while keeping it uncovered till the point cheese is",
    "melted, 10-15.",
    "Serve with your favorite toppings."
